## 六、数据结构示例

### NPC JSON 文件结构

```json
{
  "id": "lv-bu",
  "name": "吕布",
  "title": "飞将",
  "personality": "高傲、易怒、但爱才",
  "motivation": "证明自己是天下第一猛将",
  "relationships": { ... },
  "redLines": [ ... ],
  "era": "三国",
  "eraFeatures": "群雄割据、忠义、智谋"
}
```

### 事件 JSON 文件结构

```json
{
  "id": "combat",
  "name": "战斗事件",
  "type": "instant",
  "triggers": ["攻击", "刺杀", "挑战"],
  "effects": {
    "hp": -20,
    "relationship": -30
  }
}
```

### 云数据库表结构

```typescript
interface Session {
  _id: string;
  sessionId: string;        // userId_scenarioId
  userId: string;
  scenarioId: string;
  npcs: Object;
  relationships: Object;
  player: Object;
  recentSummary: string;    // 最近 3 轮
  keyEvents: Array;
  history: Array;
  createdAt: Date;
  updatedAt: Date;
}
```

